SRC/SLM/slm_vars:  The sstxy was defined for first radiation call in slm_init without subtracting t00. As the result, radiative fluxes at the first model call were screwed up.

SGS_TKE: corrected inconsistency for computation of molecular viscosity and conductivity fluxes at walls in DNS mode. 
affected fiiles:
diffuse_mom3D_DNS.f90
diffuse_scalar3D_DNS.f90
sgs.f90

SRC/SGS_TKE/sgs.f90
error in index that may cause instability of diffusion in some cases, the 
array ady may go beying its defined indexes.
was:
cy = dtn/(dy*min(ady(j),ady(j-YES3D)))**2
should be:
cy = dtn/(dy*min(ady(j),ady(j+YES3D)))**2

SRC/setgrid.f90
the doradlon was not implemented. Instead ot doradlon, dolatlon was used.
